          "_name": "content9",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section article content9\" group=\"Article\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Text Width\" name=\"innerWidth\" min=\"50\" max=\"100\" step=\"1\" value=\"100\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Line Width\" name=\"lineLength\" min=\"10\" max=\"100\" step=\"1\" value=\"25\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Line Color\" name=\"lineColor\" value=\"#149dcc\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"inner-container\" mbr-style=\"{'width': innerWidth + '%'}\">\n            <hr class=\"line\" mbr-style=\"{'width': lineLength + '%'}\">\n            <div class=\"section-text align-center mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".section-text\" mbr-text><b>Matlab and Simulink is now offered to the whole campus through Matlabs Online Portal/Campus-wide license. &nbsp;Faculty and Cadets are covered by the campus-wide license and can install software on their home or laptop computers.<br></b><br><a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/academia/tah-portal/virginia-military-institute-332647.html\" target=\"_blank\"><b>To acces VMI's Matlab portal click here</b></a><br><br><a href=\"https://vmi.box.com/s/kqq83afnkyr0shoxixpqlhg4br7tbvrk\" target=\"_blank\"><b>View Instructions here</b></a><a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/academia/tah-portal/virginia-military-institute-332647.html\" target=\"_blank\"><br></a><br><div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/learn/tutorials/matlab-onramp.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 1rem; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If you are not familiar with Matlab please complete the 2 hour Matlab Onramp tutorial that can be found on the initial portal site by scrolling down and clicking \"Start learning now\" in the MATLAB Onramp box</a><br></div><div><br></div><div><b style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">ADDITIONAL OPTIONS - MATLAB ONLINE - Can be used online through web browser</b><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><b><br></b></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">- No downloads needed</span><br></div><div>- No setup\n needed</div><div>- No installation\n needed</div><div>- No maintenance\n to maintain</div><div>- Just sign up and sign in\n</div><div>- <b>Use it anywhere, anytime, on any computer, laptop or Chromebook\n</b></div><div>- <a href=\"https://matlab.mathworks.com/\" target=\"_blank\">To access Matlab Online goto https://matlab.mathworks.com/\n</a></div><div>- Matlab is also available for mobile devices: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/matlab-mobile/id370976661\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone, iPad,</a> or <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mathworks.matlabmobile&hl=en_US\" target=\"_blank\">Android</a><br><br><div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"><b>INSTALLATION OR PROGRAM ISSUES?</b></span></div>- <a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/answers/98886-how-do-i-install-matlab\" target=\"_blank\">For Mathworks Official complete detailed installation instructions please go here&nbsp;</a><br><div><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">- If you have trouble with MATLAB, <a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/academia/tah-portal/virginia-military-institute-332647.html\" target=\"_blank\">goto the initial portal site</a> and click \"<a href=\"https://www.mathworks.com/support/contact_us.html?s_tid=tah_po_helpbutton_vmi\" target=\"_blank\">Need installation help? Contact MathWorks Support</a>\" to <b>create a support ticket as this is Mathworks recommended solution</b>. &nbsp; Alternatively you can goto the Barracks Help Desk located in C01-B in New Barracks for assistance, or if you are an engineering cadet you can see the Divisional Engineering IT Specialist in NEB 406.</span></div></div></div>\n            <hr class=\"line\" mbr-style=\"{'width': lineLength + '%'}\">\n        </div>\n        </div>\n</section>",
